location.fullValue: Ivy II Plan, Cypress Creek : Cottage Collection

data.description: Owner says SELL !!  Price Reduced ! This single story with brick exterior has a smart layout that makes great use of the available space. 3 bedrms,2 bath, 2 car garage.  Open area in the back of the home features a kitchen,dining area,and family room with Backyard access. Kitchen has a breakfast bar, gas stove ample cabinets, built in microwave and pantry. Seller upgraded with ceiling fans. Laminate Floors throughout except for in the bedrooms where there is carpet. Front yard is landscaped and has irrigation as well as a large fenced back yard  This recent and already established Lennar Home is located in one of the fastest growing cities. Just minutes to popular Lake Lavon, walking trails, shopping, parks, schools and dining.Relax or Swim laps in the community pool exclusively for Arcadia Farms Residents. Buy this 2 year old home and you do not have to worry about new construction right around you. Nice wide concrete street.This Highly sought after community is 45 min to DFW airport
